main event: A UFO report was filed regarding an unidentified phenomenon observed in Beltsville, Maryland on January 24, 1956.
interesting points: The report includes 3 photographs, two of which show distinct image features including a diagonal line and a blurry object., The first photograph has a clear diagonal streak across it., The second photograph appears to be an indistinct object that lacks definition., Page 2 includes a black and white image of the single diagonal line., The report is part of Project Blue Book.
